{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_08_03",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブイベント当日",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ本番ですね。やれることは全部やりました\n後はステージで全力を尽くすだけです",
      "startTime": 10.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "意気込みは十分のようだな。ところで、出場者の中に\n気になる名前があったんだが……",
      "startTime": 17.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.6538318635
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ユニットバトルの時、私達を挑発してきた二人組ですね\nまさかここでも顔を合わせることになるなんて",
      "startTime": 27.0999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "彼女達とは前にもいざこざがあったと聞いてる\nもし何か言われたら、すぐ俺に知らせてくれ",
      "startTime": 35.6333323162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.8536706609
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、そういうことなら\n彼女達とはさっき廊下ですれ違いましたよ",
      "startTime": 41.566664378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "「せいぜいステージで転ばないように\n気をつけることね」って皮肉を言われました",
      "startTime": 47.4999977113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.5016302428
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "手遅れだったか……\nだが挑発された割に怜は落ち着いているな",
      "startTime": 54.9999977113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "言われた時はムッとしましたよ\nでも、遙子さんのことを思い出したんです",
      "startTime": 61.9333310446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.5699748994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "ユニットバトルの時から、ずっと一緒に頑張ってくれて\n今回も、じっくり話し合ってくれて",
      "startTime": 70.1333310446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "そんな遙子さんのことを思ったら、パートナーとして\nこんな小さなことで取り乱す訳にはいかないなって",
      "startTime": 77.866664378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.7097251893
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "それに、今更何を言われたところで関係ありません\n今は遙子さんと最高のパフォーマンスをするだけです",
      "startTime": 86.9999977113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（怜も成長したな）\n（遙子さんと組んだことで、いい影響を受けたようだ）",
      "startTime": 93.8666664125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.4560085616
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに皮肉を言ってきた二人ですが、話していたら\n急に真っ青になって逃げ出したんですよ",
      "startTime": 103.1666664125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.1162352564
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたのかと思って振り返ったら\n私の後ろにニコニコ笑ってる遙子さんが立ってました",
      "startTime": 111.2333330792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか、笑顔で撃退するなんてさすが遙子さんだ",
      "startTime": 116.2381626132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.6109289808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "私も感心してしまいました。無言で相手を退散させる\n遙子さんの迫力、私も見習いたいです",
      "startTime": 127.1426361862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（そこは見習うところなのか……？）",
      "startTime": 131.3209244731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.0418086691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "そろそろ開演の時間ですね\nでは、行ってきます",
      "startTime": 137.3999956769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.8772969249
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "ユニットバトルの時に見せられなかった\n『私達』の全力のステージを観ていて下さい",
      "startTime": 143.1999966941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.1172969821
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.1172969821
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは！\nここからは私達が盛り上げていきます！",
      "startTime": 151.4666643781,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 749.3701932000079,
          "startTime": 149.9333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8733.325449299997,
          "startTime": 160.1999898274
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.4873661044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "いつもは五人だけど\n今日は私達二人のユニットで楽しんで下さいね！",
      "startTime": 156.8666430158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.6075991315
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（これは、二人の良さがよく出ているな）\n（タイプの違う二人がお互いの魅力を引き立てている）",
      "startTime": 168.7666511537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.047603512
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（これは誰にでも出来ることじゃない）\n（認め合い、高め合う二人だから出来るステージだ）",
      "startTime": 175.9666562399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.6319613777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんが私の魅力を引き出してくれる……\n一緒に頑張る仲間がいれば私はもっと成長出来る……",
      "startTime": 187.6333229066,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13366.666920799986,
          "startTime": 200.9999898274
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 193.0257577262
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "最高のステージを目指して、心を合わせて歌います\n私達二人のチームワーク、観ていて下さいね！",
      "startTime": 197.9999895733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 197.9999895733
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 204.3592758817
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（怜と遙子さん……息の合った二人のパフォーマンスに）\n（みんなが目を奪われている）",
      "startTime": 209.1999956768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 211.1463374139
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（次はどんな魅力が引き出されるのか）\n（二人の今後が楽しみだ）",
      "startTime": 214.766672516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 217.852062003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night",
      "startTime": 218.9187246007
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "昨日のイベントは、沢山いた出演者の中で\n怜達のユニットが一番盛り上がっていたな",
      "startTime": 223.4333351137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "会場のアンケートでも、断トツの人気だったそうだ",
      "startTime": 226.3614167215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "私も手応えを感じました。あの後、遙子さんとも\n前回のリベンジが出来たって話したんですよ",
      "startTime": 235.1999966941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "ユニットバトルが悔いの残る終わり方だったので\n今回は全力を出し切れて良かったです",
      "startTime": 242.9333300275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、怜達のステージが盛り上がり過ぎて\n次に歌うユニットは大変だったようだがな",
      "startTime": 250.3999966941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "私と遙子さんに噛みついてきた二人組ですね\n確かに、緊張のし過ぎでミスを連発していました",
      "startTime": 258.2333300275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "怜達の圧巻のパフォーマンスを見せられた直後だからな\nもの凄いプレッシャーを感じていたはずだ",
      "startTime": 268.0666633608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "ミスしたのは怜達のせいだと\n逆恨みされないといいが……",
      "startTime": 272.6999966941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "それは大丈夫だと思いますよ。あの後、落ち込んでる\n彼女達に遙子さんが声を掛けてましたから",
      "startTime": 279.9333300275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんが親身になって相談に乗ってあげたら\n二人とも帰る頃にはすっかり遙子さんに懐いてました",
      "startTime": 288.2999966941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei023.m4a",
      "text": "あの優しさと包容力は遙子さんらしいですね\n私には真似出来そうにありません",
      "startTime": 299.3666633608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "それでいいんじゃないか？　遙子さんには遙子さんの\n怜には怜の良さがあるんだから",
      "startTime": 307.6333300275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。私達はみんな違うから\n一緒にいて成長出来るのかもしれません",
      "startTime": 315.3666633608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "怜も遙子さんと今まで以上に打ち解けたみたいだな",
      "startTime": 318.8455443862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "おかげさまで、最近はなんでも\n遠慮なく言い合えるようになりました",
      "startTime": 325.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "今までも、遠慮していたようには見えなかったけどな",
      "startTime": 327.8857709093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei026.m4a",
      "text": "寮で時間がある時は\n遙子さんからいろんなことを教わってるんです",
      "startTime": 333.8666633608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei027.m4a",
      "text": "これからも沢山のことを教え合って、一歩一歩\nみんなと一緒に歩んで行けたらって思ってます",
      "startTime": 342.7999966941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei028.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、もうこんな時間\nレッスンがあるので私はこれで失礼しますね",
      "startTime": 349.8666633608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "分かってると思うが\nハードワークにならないよう気をつけるんだぞ",
      "startTime": 355.7666633608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei029.m4a",
      "text": "その言葉、そっくりお返しします\n{user}さんも適度に休憩して下さい",
      "startTime": 363.4999966941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-rei030.m4a",
      "text": "あ……それから、そこにあるおにぎり\n食べたかったら食べてもいいですよ",
      "startTime": 373.4333279929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、早速いただくよ\n……このおにぎり、もしかして手作りか？",
      "startTime": 381.3666796368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_03-koh021.m4a",
      "text": "……美味しい\nなるほど、怜も日々成長しているな",
      "startTime": 392.6000312807,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
